BEG: Convincing others to give you money or aid

Category: Rogue
Base skill: 25% (+4%/level, cap 98%)

Playing the part of someone desperate enough to be given money, food,
or sympathy, convincingly enough that strangers actually hand it
over. Useful for blending in as a beggar or refugee, working a crowd
for information, or getting by without resorting to theft.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, streetwise, seduction
